column5: Hey gang - I don't often post clips from The Show as I've gotten jumped on in the past for spamming... despite my continued support and participation on the board.... but I thought this was a fun clip from last summer!  We post vids like this at least once a week so check them out!  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0NK4nf_qIRE&feature=channel_video_title  Have a great week!  Ryan
The boys got a kick out of that one, when they saw the show, Ryan.  Can't wait to try out that "froggy" this summer.
those big bully frogs will eat anything they can get into thier mouths ! I saw one eat a sparrow that landed too close one time. Never had a chance
Bull frogs eat baby snapping turtles. Another frog is just softer food...

Great clip, Ryan. Imagine if that frog would have turned into a prince though. Then Ol' Dave really would have had some splainin' to do not to mention the quart of Janitor in a Drum to wash his mouth.
LOL.. thats pretty funny, and always remember, "one mans spam is another mans klik"

Hey Ryan, your dues are current, so keep bringin' 'em.  However................your boss kissing a frog is a bit kinky.  Kissing the frog that assumed the top position of a sex act is a lot kinky.  Might be a good idea to work on that one.
This one didn't like my frog invading his pad
lol say what you will about kissing frogs - Dave caught some pretty good fish that day after kissing that bull frog so if it worked for him.....
